\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Bearer
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 , stacking up to 3 times. Upon leaving the 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Enlightened Mind
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  state, all 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Bearer
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  stacks are consumed to grant the same number of 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Qingming Sword Force
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  stacks.\cb1 \
\cb30 Upon entering the battlefield, gain 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Unity
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 , increasing CRIT Rate by 
\f0\b \cf31 \strokec31 30%
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  and DMG by 
\f0\b \cf31 \strokec31 25%
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 .\cb1 \
\cb30 When 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Ultimate: Chasing Storms
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  or 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Entry Skill: Illuminating Darkness
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  is unleashed, Ye Shunguang enters the 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Enlightened Mind
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  state and activates 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Ether Veil: Verdict
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 . 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Ether Veil: Verdict
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  has the same duration as 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Enlightened Mind
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 . The duration lasts 16s, and the duration timer pauses while she is off-field. During the 
