\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 .\cb1 \
\cb30 While 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Ether Veil: Verdict
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  is active, when an enemy enters 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Ether Veil: Verdict
